title: Final Fantasy Type-0 (English Translation) PSP
description:
==================== 
Game Details 
==================== 
Filetype: 1 ISO 
Size: 2.7GB (uncompressed) 
Region: NTSC-J 
CERO Rating: C 
Language: English Translated 
Players: 1-3 Players (Ad-hoc) 
Genre: RPG 
Release Date: October 27, 2011 (JP) 
English Patch Release Date: June 8, 2014 
Developed by: Square Enix 


==================== 
Game Description 
==================== 
Experience the epic saga of the eastern lands of Orience! Switch at will between fourteen characters with unique weapons and abilities! An all new type of FINAL FANTASY! 


==================== 
Game Instructions 
==================== 
- Unrar the files 
- Place file into ISO folder of PSP 
- Play on PSP 

> This ISO file was personally tested on a  PSP and is deemed as "working" with no present bugs. Custom firmware used for this test is 6.60 PRO-B10
